 
<p>
The reason Social Security won't have enough income after 2034 is that
rich people have taken a
<a href="https://robertreich.substack.com/p/an-easy-way-to-save-social-security">much bigger fraction of all the income in the
US</a>.
 And rich people pay the social security tax on only a limited
amount of their income.

